{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<strong>Bloody Rune</strong>&quot; is a turn-based, single-stroke drawing roguelike deck-building game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal is to defeat all enemies by using the appropriate &quot;runes&quot; based on the situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/storepage_gif_1.gif?t=1729814907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Runes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Instead of simply breaking blocks, you can draw runes with the blocks to use rune skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/storepage_gif_2.gif?t=1729814907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choices</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to think about various variables, such as the runes you currently have and the enemies you will encounter next, and make synergistic choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/storepage_gif_3.gif?t=1729814907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Shop</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the shops you encounter during the game, you must decide whether to purchase stronger runes right away or save your money to buy even more powerful runes at the next shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/extras/storepage_gif_4.gif?t=1729814907\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bloody Rune is developed by Solutena, a solo developer, who has created all the elements of the game\u2014including design, programming, art, effects, and music\u2014without using any assets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the game!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Won!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/9010f60e5b1ff560215e331a93a25aabe14f4faf.jpg"},{"name":"That's too much","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/ac80786a3ef1e9b9cce305b46c20d064079b9410.jpg"},{"name":"Get ready","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/349a2b4ccccffd1d25dad154d575e939804fa3c2.jpg"},{"name":"No way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/7317fb2258b9d37be6a7ed26514438d685778850.jpg"},{"name":"I\u2019m going to be rich","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/2e10f0d513abd1494d99d3db02f20bf7d0ec0771.jpg"},{"name":"I have it too","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/573531058aa2965da5b3f2aed29784dcb653e229.jpg"},{"name":"Just passing by","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/9038daca6ebbc43cf96488eae05bb84bac3c8af3.jpg"},{"name":"That's enough","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/7497ba03747310eaca8fd8206be306c810b8e4f8.jpg"},{"name":"It's poisonous","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/f763db479d64a3a51e7fabaaa79df62fbb4e2649.jpg"},{"name":"Whoosh whoosh clink clink","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3152660/c921dba821648050ecc9c42c44f467a86284f8ac.jpg"}],"total":12},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729814907","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152660/page.bg.jpg?t=1729814907","capsule_i